<view class="rounded-[32rpx] border border-slate-100/70 bg-white/90 p-5 shadow-[0_20px_45px_rgba(15,23,42,0.08)] data-v-f036cb06"><view class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[6rpx] text-slate-400 data-v-f036cb06"> 条件编译 </view><view class="text-2xl font-semibold text-slate-900 data-v-f036cb06"> css-macro 语法在模板中的实际效果 </view><view class="mt-4 space-y-4 data-v-f036cb06"><view class="text-sm text-neutral-600 data-v-f036cb06"> 依赖 weapp-tailwindcss/css-macro 进行条件编译 </view><view class="rounded-[24rpx] border border-dashed border-slate-200 bg-slate-50/80 p-4 text-sm text-slate-600 data-v-f036cb06"><view class="mb-2 text-neutral-400 data-v-f036cb06"> 样式的条件编译 <text class="text-sky-400 underline data-v-f036cb06" bindtap="{{a}}"> weapp-tailwindcss/css-macro </text></view><view class="rounded-xl px-3 py-2 text-white ifdef-[MP-WEIXIN]:bg-blue-500 ifndef-[MP-WEIXIN]:bg-red-500 data-v-f036cb06"> 微信小程序为蓝色，不是微信小程序为红色 </view><view class="mt-3 rounded-xl px-3 py-2 text-white wx:bg-blue-500 -wx:bg-red-500 data-v-f036cb06"><view class="data-v-f036cb06">自定义配置的方式进行样式条件编译</view><view class="data-v-f036cb06">相关配置见根目录下的 tailwind.config.ts</view></view><view class="mt-3 rounded-xl bg-white/60 px-3 py-2 text-slate-700 data-v-f036cb06"><view class="apply-class-0 data-v-f036cb06"> @apply 条件编译方式0 </view><view class="apply-class-1 data-v-f036cb06"> @apply 条件编译方式1 </view></view></view></view><view class="mt-4 rounded-[24rpx] border border-slate-200/80 bg-white/60 p-4 shadow-inner data-v-f036cb06"><view class="text-sm font-semibold text-slate-700 data-v-f036cb06"> 更多文档 </view><view class="text-xs text-slate-500 data-v-f036cb06"> 点击复制链接 </view><view class="mt-3 flex flex-wrap gap-2 text-xs data-v-f036cb06"><view class="rounded-full bg-slate-900/5 px-3 py-1 font-semibold text-slate-600 data-v-f036cb06" bindtap="{{b}}"> 官网 </view><view class="rounded-full bg-slate-900/5 px-3 py-1 font-semibold text-slate-600 data-v-f036cb06" bindtap="{{c}}"> Guide </view></view></view></view>